                        </extent>
                        <collation>1–38<hi rend="superscript">8</hi>, 39<hi rend="superscript">8</hi>(6–8 canc.); catchwords; quire-signatures of the usual late medieval form. The quires numbered at the beginning, s. xvii.</collation>
